.DT
add_wear_effect
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_wear_effect

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_wear_effect -  This method adds a new wear effect to the current wear effect array.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_wear_effect(string effect)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^effect%^RESET%^ - the effect to add
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/wearable.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a new wear effect to the current wear effect array.
These effects will automaticly be added when worn and removed when
taken off.
They will only be removed if the effect has the
person_removing_item() function in it.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_wear_effects(), set_wear_effects(), person_removing_item()

.EP

